     ----------------------------------------------------------------------

    FOOTBALL DIRECTOR 2:

	U selekcionom  meniju  drzhi pritsnute  tastere 'Ctrl' i 'C' da bi
	zaustavio  program.  Upishi "AI=AI+500000"  (ili "AI+AI+500000") i
	pritsni 'Return'.  Upishi "CONT"  i pritisni 'Return'.  Ovo dodaje
	500 000 kredita tvojoj trenutnoj sumi.

     ----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
@node 387 ""
